latestPosts.caption:
Me Casually talking to my younger Self and realising how far we have come ! 
.
Let me be clear it’s not always the achievements that matter but also how we take care our mental health is the “BIGGEST ACHIEVEMENT “ in itself 
.
Let’s do it not for our fathers , mothers , sisters , brothers but for that child who was left alone , abandoned and often felt unworthy of love . We owe that child a good and happy future 🙏

I am still on the way and I have a long long way to go but this reel is to simply appreciate myself for standing strong all this while 👍❤️🧿
